William G. Schilling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_G._Schilling 0 William G. Schilling (born August 30, 1939 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania) is a retired American actor of film and television. He played Dr. Harold Samuels on the television series Head of the Class between 1986 and 1991.
